remarks.summary: On Friday, 2 February: Strike at 15 transport operators
remarks.text: In Berlin at BVG from approx. 3 a.m. to 10 a.m., in Brandenburg all day. This affects underground trains, trams and buses. Long-distance and regional trains as well as S-Bahn trains will run as scheduled. Info: www.vbb.de/streik and www.bvg.de
